<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, October 30 (Xinhua) -- Mozambican Ministry of
Environmental Co-ordination issued a press communique here Friday
canceling its decision which allows the International Waste Group
Limited to import, export, transport and store waste in the
country.
</P>
