<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, October 31 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait and Switzerland
signed an agreement here Saturday aimed at protecting and
encouraging bilateral investments.
</P>
<P>
The 15-year deal, which is automatically renewable, was inked
by Kuwaiti Minister of Finance and Communication Sheikh Ali
Al-Salem Al-Sabah and Head of the Swiss Federal Office for
External Economic Relations Franz Blankart.
</P>
<P>
