stable political situation create favorable environment for
developing more economic projects.
</P>
<P>
Blankart, heading a Swiss businessmen delegation from chemical,
foodstuff, machinery, watch-making industries and banking sector,
arrived here Friday on a three-day visit.
</P>
<P>
They will travel on to the United Arab Emirates Sunday evening
after wrapping up their visit in Kuwait. 
