<P>
Paris: min. 6 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 5 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 7 degrees C., max. 13 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze. 
</P>
