<HEADLINE> Iraq-UNSCOM 1st Add ... by President Saddam Hussein. </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The joint meeting said the decision would not be applied
to the International Atomic Energy Agency (IAEA), another U.N.
agency assigned with the mission of counting for and destroying
Iraq's nuclear weapons.
</P>
<P>
Iraq decides to freeze all UNSCOM's activities in Iraq
