<HEADLINE> EC President Jacques Santer Leaves for Wuhan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 31 (Xinhua) -- President of the European
Commission (EC) Jacques Santer and his party left here this
afternoon for Wuhan, capital of Central China's Hubei
Province, to continue his China trip.
</P>
<P>
During his stay in Beijing, Santer met with Chinese
President Jiang Zemin, Li Peng, chairman of the Chinese National
People's Congress Standing Committee, Premier Zhu Rongji, and other
officials.
</P>
